# filter.db controls optional event filtering in evio_parser.
# Each non-comment row is: rocid slot module bank
# With -PFILTER:ENABLE=1, evio_parser keeps only payload that matches
# the rocid+bank combinations listed here.
# The slot and module columns are currently informational (not enforced).
# They are kept for readability and possible future slot/module filtering.
# rocid slot  module   bank
  1      3    250    250
  1      3    9250   9250
  1     21    9001   9001
  1     14    3654   3654

